      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COSTLY HABITS (5) shows ability but remains a maiden after 12 starts. Was in the placings again last time finishing second (18.25) at this track. Has good box speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Capable of going well again. MISS PEACHY (1) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 12 length fifth (18.76) at this track in a Maiden. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Key chance on best form. CRIKEY MATE (7) has been close to a win, finishing in the minors three on end before a fourth when checked in the run last time in a Grade 6/MDN at Gawler (23.93). Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Key chance on best form. OPAL LIMES (3) collected a minor prize last start over this track and distance - must be considered.",
